des: Control your monitor by using Alexa with 5Gencare of Chillaxcare App. Use Alexa with your ChillaxCare account to manage your home and baby camera monitors. The official Alexa skill allows to select different monitor to check Temperature, play or stop lullabies from the monitor and change speaker volume of monitor.
